<h1>About Us</h1>
<p>
    We believe that it is far too difficult for people to find short-term work. <a href="http://workdemanded.com/">WorkDemanded</a>
    is a web service that enables users to easily find short-term work that needs to be done nearby. 

We aggregate jobs from marketplaces such as <a href="http://craigslist.org/">Craigslist</a>, <a href="http://taskrabbit.com/">TaskRabbit</a>, <a href="http://gigwalk.com/">Gigwalk</a> and <a href="http://zaarly.com/">Zaarly</a>, among many others, and present the data to users in a way that is relevant and actionable. Jobs on WorkDemanded include delivery, driving, event help, garbage removal, handyman work, house chores, office help, modeling, moving, and shopping. Whether you're a high school student interested in making some extra pocket change, or a full-time freelancer that needs to maintain a close pulse on the work demanded in the region, we're your one stop shop. Tweet us <a
